		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There is no "cheating on" the NES unless you're being paid. Work on what you want to work on. Even I have time to make nearly 7000 posts over at <a href="http://forum.gbadev.org/" class="postlink">That Other Board</a>.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
